function search(nums,target):
    left=0
    right=nums.length - 1

    while left <=right:
        mid=(left+right)/ 2

        if nums[mid]==target:
            return mid

        if nums[left] <=nums[mid]:
            if nums[left] <=target < nums[mid]:
                right=mid - 1
            else:
                left=mid+1
        else:
            if nums[mid] < target <=nums[right]:
                left=mid+1
            else:
                right=mid - 1

    return -1

```

This runs in O(logn)time and O(1)space(excluding input).

