function binarySearch(arr,target,low,high):
    if low > high:
        return -1
    mid=(low+high)/ 2
    if arr[mid]==target:
        return mid
    else if arr[mid] < target:
        return binarySearch(arr,target,mid+1,high)else:
        return binarySearch(arr,target,low,mid - 1)
```

Recurrence: T(n)=T(n/2)+O(1)gives T(n)=O(logn).

Problem: Find k-th smallest without fully sorting.
Approach: Partition like quicksort,recurse only one side.
