function singleNumber(nums):
    xorAll=0
    for num in nums:
        xorAll=xorAll XOR num

    // xorAll=a XOR b
    // Find rightmost set bit
    rightmostBit=xorAll &(-xorAll)a=0,b=0
    for num in nums:
        if(num & rightmostBit)!=0:
            a=a XOR num
        else:
            b=b XOR num

    return [a,b]

```

O(n)time,O(1)space(excluding input). Two passes through the array.

